descriptionHtml:
Hey! This is my first save game on Nexus.

About the character:

Name: Timo
Race: Argonian
Location: Solitude
Level: 3
Skill Points: 2 (I didn't spend the skill points)
Health: 120
Stamina: 100
Magicka: 100 (130 with ring)

This save is for people who want to skip the intro.
You still can edit my character with the command 'showracemenu' but !ALERT! it can maybe cause bugs if you change the race. If you only change the looking, everything should be fine.
